  "instructions": [
    "Peel and dice the pineapple.",
    "Dice the chili peppers and finely chop tarragon leaves.",
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat. Add garlic cloves and spices blend, cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add diced chili peppers, pineapple, and tarragon to the pan. Cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "Transfer mixture into a bowl, drizzle with glaze sauce and mix well.",
    "Heat vegetable oil in another pan over medium heat. Place the wrap bread on it and cook until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Place the cooked wrap bread on a plate, top with the pineapple-tarragon chili mixture.",
    "Serve hot."
